This sheet identifies the GCODES tables that provide descriptions of codes returned for DataScope Select fields. To view content descriptions:
1. Access the GCODES View on MyAccount. Note that access to this site requires user registration.

2. Links to tables listed alphabetically are provided. Click on the letter representing the table name. The table name preceeds "_cds."  The text that follows, ending in descr, identifes the table column where the values are identified.
3. Locate the description in the description column.
